{"tid":1473723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係咁快唔撚記得721呀？做野啦！","createTime":"2019-08-15T02:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T04:08:10.000Z","uid":222268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"365916412866b86d2bffff17eead8ece3b941d15","tid":1473723,"uid":222268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:34:38.000Z","msg":"機場單野令大家就黎唔記得之前既野，<br />\n下面有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">建築師</span></span>教路，畫尻晒圖俾你地做<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">超合作運動，付出少，合法有效果，唔撚係唔去呀嘛！</span></span>？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n之前有唔少嘅超合作舉報行動，係時候進行下一波。有建築師朋友整咗呢兩張圖，集合咗常見嘅違例建築。希望大家廣傳出去，將呢個行動擴展至全港！<br />\n<br />\n市民如遇&rdquo;懷疑&rdquo;違例建築物可以以下途徑舉報：<br />\n<br />\n屋宇署熱線  2626 1616（由「1823」接聽）<br />\n1823 電話中心 1823 （24小時運作）<br />\n網上舉報  電子舉報表格 （網上表格&lt;<a href=\"https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/bd0001/tc/&gt;）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feform.one.gov.hk%2Fform%2Fbd0001%2Ftc%2F%3E%EF%BC%89&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=6a78ab27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/bd0001/tc/&gt;）</a> <a href=\"https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/bd0001/tc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feform.one.gov.hk%2Fform%2Fbd0001%2Ftc%2F&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=ddd7d4e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/bd0001/tc/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你發現有走火通道阻塞，可以致電消防處投訴熱線：2723 8787<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住，舉報係可以匿名進行㗎！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/twsGZZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtwsGZZ7.jpg&h=0b1f2a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTHf4so.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTHf4so.jpg&h=43c2b1fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img sr